msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/complete"
msgid "Congratulations, you have finished the first tutorial (basic infantry control)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/date"
msgid "June 22nd, 1941 · Border with the USSR"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/help"
msgid "Re-watch steps"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/hint"
msgid "Press this button to re-watch the video for this tutorial phase."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/name"
msgid "Tutorial 1: Infantry Control"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/name_big"
msgid "Infantry Control"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/00"
msgid "About time! Park the truck and unload!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/01"
msgid "Soldaten! Welcome to the \"Ostfront\"! You are now in the front line. If you want to remain in one piece, you will follow all my orders to the letter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/02"
msgid "The first thing you need to know as infantrymen, is to ALWAYS seek cover. In the open, you are vulnerable. Cover improves your survivability and your aim. Now, take cover behind the sandbags."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/03"
msgid "We seem to be clear... MG team 1, stay here. Everyone else, forward, take positions on the stone wall. Los gehts!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/04"
msgid "The Bolsheviks will be coming down that road any minute now. We will ambush them. Soldaten, get ready!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/05"
msgid "Alright, I can see the Ivans! Hold your fire until they're in front of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/06"
msgid "Now, give them hell!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/07"
msgid "Very good. You have achieved your first kills. The more kills you achieve, the higher your veterancy. You will improve your shooting and survival skills."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/08"
msgid "Our neighboring squad has found a pocket of resistance up ahead. There is an MG pinning our boys down. We are behind them! I need you to get close and throw a grenade on that MG nest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/09"
msgid "Well done, men! Finish these Ivans off!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/10"
msgid "Look at that, the Ivans have unwillingly brought us a truck! Go and look if it has any weaponry we can loot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/11"
msgid "Damn it! There's a soviet tank ambushing us from the other side of the farm! Get behind it and destroy it with the AT grenades that you have acquired."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/12"
msgid "Good job! Blown to smithereens! Now finish off the remaining infantry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/13"
msgid "Enemy armored car coming down the road!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/14"
msgid "Fortunately, we are prepared for this. Take command of the AT rifleman, and turn that armored car into Swiss cheese!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/ger_officer/15"
msgid "Well done, men! You have completed my instructions to the letter. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/01"
msgid "Welcome to boot camp, Soldier. In this tutorial, you will learn how to control infantry, the most common and important type of unit on the battlefield."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/01b"
msgid "During a cutscene, you cannot control your units. Some cutscenes, like this one, can be skipped. To do so, press the \"continue\" button on the top-right corner."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/02"
msgid ""
"To move your soldier, select him and right-click on the destination. A double click will make him sprint until his stamina runs out. If you move your cursor close "
"to objects, it will prompt the soldier to take cover, previewing a silhouette. Now, make your soldier take cover with the rest of the men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/03"
msgid "Well done. You should always move your troops from one cover to the next. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/04"
msgid ""
"Approach the MG nest carefully from behind. Move from one bush or cover to the next. A prone soldier will be harder to spot. When the MG nest is taken out, the rest "
"of the squad will assist you in taking out the remaining Soviets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/05"
msgid ""
"Select your soldier, and press 'X' or click on the 'examine' icon. When you hover over the vehicle, the cursor will change to an eye. Transfer any AT grenades from "
"the inventory of the truck to your soldier's inventory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/06"
msgid "Infantry can move in any terrain, but vehicles, especially wheeled vehicles, must use roads to travel at maximum speed, which makes them easy to ambush."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/07"
msgid ""
"Buildings and other objects block the line of sight of units. You can see the enemy tank because other friendly units are actively fighting it. But no enemy "
"unit is currently able to see your soldier. Because of this, you can easily flank the enemy tank without being detected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/08"
msgid "You must be aware of your mission objectives. You can always open your mission tasks with the hotkey \"O\"."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/narrator/scene/09"
msgid ""
"Quite often, you will need to get rid of remaining enemies to proceed with the next stages of a mission. Keep an eye out for enemies who may be concealed in "
"the \"fog of war\", for example, hiding in trenches."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Mission Accomplished!\n\n"
"Click on 'continue' to keep playing this mission or click on 'next' to proceed directly into the next mission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/place"
msgid "Army Group Centre"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/story"
msgid ""
"Welcome to boot camp, Soldier.\n\n"
"In this tutorial, you will learn how to control infantry, the most common and important type of unit in the battlefield.\n\n"
"                                        Good luck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task1"
msgid "Take cover behind the sandbags."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task2"
msgid "Take cover behind the stone wall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task3"
msgid "Eliminate the Soviet border patrol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task4"
msgid "Take out the MG nest with a grenade."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task5"
msgid "Retrieve AT grenades from the Soviet truck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task6"
msgid "Destroy the Soviet tank with the AT grenades."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/01_inf-control/task7"
msgid "Eliminate the armored car with the AT rifle."
msgstr ""
